comments: Debbie is one of the most enthusiastic, bubbly, and helpful people you will meet in your life. She makes Intro to FACS super easy. All 3 exams are online and the group project is a piece of cake. The class meets once a week, so make sure you go as attendance is mandatory.
Mrs. Debbie is the absolute best!!!! Best professor by far! Take her class and you will be the happiest person ever!

Dr. Debbie is so incredibly enthusiastic & thoroughly enjoys the property mgmt industry. She tries her hardest to make the material easy to understand. DO NOT BUY THE BOOK- never opened mine. there are 5 quizzes (she tells you the answers), no tests, speaker summaries & small assignments. great class, she even says it will be an easy A!
Awesome class. Easy A. She even said it was a GPA booster. Definitely take if you get the chance. All you need to do in class is Facebook and play on your computer. Enjoy and take if possible

Very fun, engaging professor. Has a ton of real world experience to back up her teaching. The knowledge shares and speaker summaries are awesome as they help to reinforce the material we learn in class. The class itself is awesome. I love HACE in general.
If Debbie taught all of my classes, I would be okay with that. She\'s the most positive person I\'ve ever met, and so passionate about her job. TAKE THIS CLASS. SO EASY.
I think that she is a bubble bright soul... god bless her heart!!! you should take this class just for fun because she makes learning about housing fun!
If you passed your high school P.E. class, you are pretty much guaranteed an A in this class. Easiest class I have taken since middle school.
TAKE THIS CLASS! IM TELLING YOU
